#### h2-section-block ####
header: Learning Materials for Software Developers
----
body:

Software developers are lifelong learners. Most of them like it, the others are forced by the software industry.

Learning materials for software developers can be a good choice to please them. If you prefer this way you have two options: Programming books and online courses.
----
content:

##### h3-section-block #####
header: Books for Software Developers
-----
body:

It's true that software development technologies are constantly evolving, and for books, it can be tough to keep up with latest trends.

But, there are some timeless books, they are always valid and enlightening.

So you can consider buying one of the software development books which I will recommend below. 

The other good thing about buying these books are they are not technology dependent. So you don't need to run an investigation about the technologies that your developer is working on.
-----
